<item>
            <title>[LU-2686] Kernel update for 3.7.2-201.fc18</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2686</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;FC18 has released a update kernel 3.7.2-201.fc18. Looks like FC18 not just use 3.6 kernel. Maybe also use 3.8 or 3.9 in future. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="17319">LU-2686</key>
            <summary>Kernel update for 3.7.2-201.fc18</summary>
